# EcoMind MVP

This is a simple Flask MVP for the EcoMind startup idea.

## Project Overview

EcoMind is an AI-powered sustainability platform that helps individuals and businesses reduce their carbon footprint by providing personalized recommendations for energy-efficient practices, waste reduction, and eco-friendly product alternatives.

## Run Instructions

1. Clone the repository: `git clone https://github.com/your-username/ecomind-mvp.git`
2. Create a virtual environment: `python -m venv env`
3. Activate the virtual environment: `source env/bin/activate` (on Linux/Mac) or `env\Scripts\activate` (on Windows)
4. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`
5. Run the application: `python app.py`
6. Access the API endpoints at `http://localhost:5000`

## API Endpoints

* `GET /users`: Get a list of users
* `GET /recommendations`: Get a list of sustainability recommendations
* `POST /users`: Create a new user
